<p>Or, in other words, a proxy for the weight of her companionship, fashioned in zinc and copper.</p>
<p>Spare change rattles echoes of our sacrificial rites of womanhood.</p>
<p>So I am a collector of the most mundane of heirlooms.</p>
<p>
